ttp://matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html">ROGUE</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> : <br><br>1 - PoH &gt; ground pop near Maestro &gt; raid KGC<br>2 - Steamfont Mountain &gt; Renux &gt; Divers loots &gt; 3 groupes<br>3 - Kithikor &gt; General V'Ghera &gt; guild event <br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.angelflame.com/ranger/epic.html">RANGER</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- CoM &gt; Reavers to get a jade reaver &gt; raid<br>- Karnor &gt; VSR to get a sickly pulsating stone&gt; Camp+raid<br>- PoH &gt; minobosses to get a Shattered Emerald of Corruption<br>- PoA &gt; island 4 to get a swirling globe<br>1 - EK &gt; Dark Elf Corruptor &gt; 2 groups<br>2 - Hole &gt; Jael the wretched to get a Soulbound Hammer &gt; raid<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqdruids.com/epic_quests/epic_main.htm">DRUID</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>- Kedge Keep &gt; Corrupted Seahorse &gt; 2 Groups<br>- Ocean of Tears &gt; Corrupted Cyclops &gt; 2 Groups<br>- Lesser Faydark &gt; Corrupted Brownie &gt; 1 Group<br>- CoM &gt; Reavers to get a jade reaver &gt; raid<br>- Karnor &gt; VSR to get a sickly pulsating stone&gt; Camp+raid<br>1 - Swamp of No Hope &gt; Ulump Pujik &gt; 2 groups<br>2 - Timorous Deep &gt; Dragon Faydedar &gt; raid<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.graffe.com/quests/fiery_avenger_type/">WIZZARD</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> : <br><br>- Kedge &gt; Phinigel(Blue Crystal Staff) &gt; camp+raid<br>- Karnor &gt; VS (Gnarled Staff ) &gt; raid KGC<br>- PoF &gt; Broken Golem, make Enraged Golem pop (green oil) &gt; raid KGC (He double hits for 400 and has around 150k hp)<br>(Alt to the broken golem is :<br>1 - PoF &gt; Cazic Thule (Cazic's skin) &gt; raid KGC<br>2 - Sebilis &gt; Tolapumj (powder) &gt; raid)<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.angelflame.com/cleric/cleric_epic.html">CLERIC</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> : <br><br>- Chardock &gt; Overking Bathezid(singed scroll) &gt; raid<br>1 - Temple of Ro &gt; Prismatic priest &gt; small raid<br>2 - BW &gt; Ixiblat Fer(scepter of Ixiblat) &gt; raid<br>- Skyfire &gt; Ragefire &gt; raid<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.bjornstar.com/">ENCHANTER</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- Chardock &gt; Prince (head) &gt; raid<br>- Cabilis &gt; Vessel Drozlin (xolion rod) &gt; raid<br>- Neriak &gt; Verina Tomb (Innoruuk's word) &gt; raid<br>- PoA &gt; Ground pop near an Effreti &gt; raid KGC<br>- CoM &gt; Wraith of Jaxion (to be charmed to hand him the dull ruby) &gt; raid<br>- PoF &gt; Shissar Spirit(spawn after CT death) &gt; raid KGC<br>- PoH &gt; male&amp;female revenants (essence of vampire) &gt; raid KGC<br>- Hole &gt; Ghost of Kindle &gt; raid<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.sbow.net/quests/epics/nec.html">NECROMANCER</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- PoA &gt; PoA quest (Cloak of Spiroc Feathers) &gt; Several raids (to be confirmed)<br>- PoF &gt; Golems (blood of Cazic Thule) &gt; raid KGC<br>- PoH &gt; minibosses (eye of Innoruuk) &gt; raid KGC<br>1 - Chardock &gt; Herbalist (Manisi Herb) &gt; raid<br>2 - Lake Rathe &gt; 3 Mobs (symbol of insanity on the last one) &gt; raid<br>3 - PoA &gt; Gorgalosk isle &gt; raid KGC<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqdiva.com/quests/epic/default.asp">BARD</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- Kedge &gt; Phinigel(backbone) &gt; camp+raid<br>- PoF &gt; Amygdalan warrior(Amygdalan tendril) &gt; raid KGC<br>- Get red scale (Nagafen, Talendor, Nortlav Scalekeeper in Hole) &gt; raid<br>- Get white scale (Vox, Goronaire) &gt; raid<br>- Sebilis &gt; Trakanon2 &gt; raid<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://members.tripod.com/epicquestadventures/Paladin/paladin_epic_index.htm">PALADIN</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- PoF (PoH?) &gt; Thought Destroyer (Tainted DarkSteel Breastplate) &gt; raid KGC<br>- Hole &gt; Keeper of the Tombs (Tainted Sword) &gt; raid<br>- Nektulos &gt; Kirak Vil lvl55 immune vs magic (Shield) &gt; raid<br>A1 - MM &gt; Xicotl (Hilt of Soulfire) &gt; 2 groups<br>A2 - Soufire quest<br>B1- Get book of fire (Nagafen, Faydedar, Talendor, Severilous) &gt; raid<br>B1- Get book of frost (Vox, Faydedar, Goronaire) &gt; raid<br>B2 - Everfrost &gt; Lich of Miragul &gt; Need high level chanter to charm him<br>Pop Miragul(Miragul's Head and Miragul's Robe) &gt; raid (very hard necro)<br>C - PoA &gt; Pegasus island with someone in hall quest<br><br>Alternative for HIE PAL 55+:<br>- PoH &gt; The Corruptor of Life(Skull of Corruptor) &gt; raid KGC<br>- WL &gt; Corrupted Panther, Corrupted Faun, Corrupted Unicorn &gt; raid <br>.....Corrupted Panther : lvl 55 mob that can triple hit for 200, need tash<br>.....Corrupted Faun : lvl 57 mob with very low magic resist, but deals a lot of damage<br>.....Corrupted Unicorn : lvl 60 mob, very tough, shadowknight with a pet, and harm touches for 1k damage, casts blindness, very high magic resist and doubles for 350 dmg<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://matt.waggoner.com/orbofmastery.html">MAGICIAN</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> : <br><br>- CoM &gt; Neh Ashiir(Torch of the elements) &gt; raid<br>- PoH &gt; Magi P'Tasa (Staff of EM: Earth) &gt; raid KGC<br>- Kedge &gt; Phinigel (Staff of EM: Water) &gt; camp+raid<br>- OT &gt; Captain Rottgrim (Tears of Erollisi) &gt; small raid<br>- PoA &gt; island 7 (Crown of EM) &gt; raid KGC<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=768">WARRIOR</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- PoF &gt; Golems (ball of everliving Golem) &gt; raid KGC<br>- Chardock &gt; Queen (ancient blade) &gt; raid<br>- Get green dragon scale (Severilous)<br>- Get red dragon scale (Nagafen, Talendor, Nortlav Scalekeeper in Hole) &gt; raid<br>- PoH &gt; Hand of Maestro (hand of maestro) &gt; raid KGC<br>- PoA &gt; Lord Spiroc (Spiroc Wingblade) &gt; raid KGC<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.gameznet.com/eq/quest/skepicquest.html">SHADOWKNIGHT</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> :<br><br>- OT &gt; Kurron (Note to Duriek) &gt; 2 groups<br>- Hole &gt; ratman guards (tome) &gt; raid or group<br>- PoA &gt; blade of abbrogation &gt; raid KGC<br>- PoF &gt; Soul Leech &gt; raid KGC<br>1 - Hole &gt; mimics(key) &gt; raid or group<br>2 - Hole &gt; Caradorn and Kyrenna(Blood of Kyrenna, the Heart of Kyrenna) &gt; raid or 2 groups<br>3 - Hole &gt; Mummy of Glohnor(mummy wrappings of Glohnor, head of Glohnor) &gt; raid (very tough mob)<br>4 - CoM &gt; Lhranc(shk epic) &gt; raid<br><br>Only steps requiring guild or alliance help are shown here. You are very welcome to write and post the whole process for your epic :)   <p><table><tr><td><img src="http://www.ifrance.com/chimaera-res/Games/EQMryl/MrylSign04.jpg"></td><td><font color="AA0A02">Priestess of Innoruuk, 56th circle<br></font>I will save your wretched life, so you can live a long and a full of suffering life.<br>This pleases my God.<br></td></tr></table></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub64.ezboard.com/umryldainky.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mryl da Inky</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ifrance.com/chimaera-res/Games/EQMryl/dot.gif" BORDER=0> at: 3/28/02 11:47:06 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub64.ezboard.com/ftavernheroesfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=1.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub64.ezboard.com/ftavernheroesfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=1.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub64.ezboard.com/ftavernheroesfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub64.ezboard.com/ftavernheroesfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.co